<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Create Bot</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-Zenh87qX5JnK2Jl0vWa8Ck2rdkQ2Bzep5IDxbcnCeuOxjzrPF/et3URy9Bv1WTRi" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>

<body>
<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
  <div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="navbar-brand">CrypTerminator</div>
    <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNavAltMarkup" aria-controls="navbarNavAltMarkup" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
      <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
    </button>
    <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNavAltMarkup">
      <div class="navbar-nav">
        <%= link_to 'Home', root_path, class: 'nav-link'%>
        <%= link_to 'Your Bots', bots_path, class: 'nav-link'%>
        <%= link_to 'New Bot', new_bot_path, class: 'nav-link'%>
        <div style="padding-left: 1000px;"><%= link_to 'Logout', '/logout', class: 'nav-link' %></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>
<div class = "row" style="padding-top: 15px">
<div class="col-md-4 justify-content-center">
<iframe src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/Timx3-EEqzs?enablejsapi=1&amp;autoplay=1' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen height="280"
        width="498" ></iframe>
<p>If you are a beginner in crypto trading, here is a simple way you can make $100 a day easily, by trading bitcoin. here is one insanely easy exponential moving average ( ema ) strategy that you can use over and over and over again to profit on any type of cryptocurrency you wish to trade.
  This is my most used trading strategy that does not require much thinking or anything crazy do to with technical analysis, so if this strategy helped you, please</p>
<div>
  <div class="card" style="width: 27rem;">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h1>Coin Theorist</h1>
        <table class="table table-striped col-md-12" id="bot_output">
          <tr>
            <th>Attribute</th>
            <th>Value</th>
          </tr>
          <% if @edu.id == 1 %>
            <tr>
              <td>Ema 1</td>
                <td>9</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Ema 2</td>
              <td>14</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Ema 3</td>
              <td>21</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Ema 4</td>
              <td>55</td>
            </tr>
          <% else %>
            <% @edu.attributes.each do |key, value| %>
              <% unless %w[description username id updated_at youtube_id channel link created_at].include? key %>
                <tr>
                  <%  if !value.nil? %>
                    <td><%=  key  %></td>
                      <td><%= value %></td>
                  <%  end  %>
                </tr>
              <% end %>
            <% end %>
          <% end %>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<% if @edu.run %>
  <%= link_to 'Stop BackTest', edus_stoptest_path(@edu), class: 'btn btn-primary'%>
<% else %>
  <%= link_to 'BackTest this bot', edus_backtest_path(@edu), class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
<% end %>
</div>
<% if @edu.run %>
    <div class="col-md-8" style="padding-left: 50px">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
          <div>
            <div class="card" style="width: 27rem;">
              <div class="card">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h1>Profit Net Loss</h1>
                  <table class="table table-striped col-md-12" id="edu_output">

                    <%= line_chart @chart_data_pnl, label: "PNL", ytitle: "PNL", height: "200px" %>

                  </table>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
          <div class="card" style="width: 27rem;">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h1>Win Rate</h1>
                <table class="table table-striped col-md-12" id="edu_output">

                  <%= line_chart @chart_data_wr, label: "WR", ytitle: "WR", height: "200px"%>

                </table>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
          <div class="h-100 d-flex align-items-center" style="backdrop-filter: blur(5px);">
            <div class="align-items-center">
              <div class="card" style="width: 27rem;">
                <div class="card">
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h1>Trade Count</h1>
                    <table class="table table-striped col-md-12" id="bot_output">

                      <%= line_chart @chart_data_tc, label: "TC", ytitle: "TC", height: "200px" %>

                    </table>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
<% end %>
</body>
</html>